{"tid":2053322,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JYP真係一間埋沒人才既良心公司","createTime":"2020-06-06T07:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T08:51:23.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a506b97453cc7fa8b0b1a50d18eb988e579c047d","tid":2053322,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1731592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1731592&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=70355890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1731592</a><br />\n在南韓演藝圈中，不管是想要成為歌手或是偶像，都必定會經歷一段很長的練習生生活，這段時間不僅成為明星們花路上的養分也是一輩子忘不掉的回憶。近日，有一位名叫Golden的男歌手登上了《韓國好聲音2020》<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">透露自己曾在JYP娛樂練習了很長一段時間</span></span></strong>，而他一開口獨特的嗓音也立刻征服了現場所有人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4922/d4922847.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4922%2Fd4922847.jpg&h=7796bd98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Golden。（圖／翻攝自ig）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歌手Golden目前是朴宰範旗下「H1GHR MUSIC」的歌手</span></span></strong>，在這之前他有著另外一個藝名「G.Soul」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">並在JYP娛樂旗下當了長達15年的練習生生活</span></span></strong>，他在年僅13歲時參加節目《朴軫永的人才養成計劃-99%》，被社長朴軫永相中，由於它獨特的R&amp;B嗓音深受讚賞，於是<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">朴軫永便把他送到美國深造</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4922/d4922841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4922%2Fd4922841.jpg&h=b1f9b41f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Golden曾和朴軫永一起上節目。（圖／翻攝自ig）<br />\n<br />\n在美國深造期間，G.Soul還攻讀了心理學，原本有出道的機會，卻因為種種原因之下苦熬了10幾年，回到南韓後終於在2015年出道，獨特的嗓音確實在當地音樂界掀起不小的炫風，2年過後合約到期，他便離開JYP與H1GHR MUSIC簽約，接著便入伍當兵了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4922/d4922842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4922%2Fd4922842.jpg&h=3f76b3fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Golden（右）現在加入朴宰範旗下H1GHR MUSIC。（圖／翻攝自ig）<br />\n<br />\n退伍後，G.Soul將藝名改成Golden，近日以本名「金志賢」參加《韓國好聲音2020》，選擇唱李素羅的經典歌曲《拜託》，一開口就讓導師寶兒、Dynamic Duo按鈕轉身，隨後連副歌都還沒有唱完，剩下兩位導師金鍾國、成始璄也立即轉身，獨特的嗓音與轉音讓所有人眼睛都為之一亮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4922/d4922845.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4922%2Fd4922845.jpg&h=35b3bae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Golden登上《韓國好聲音2020》，導師們爭相按鈕。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n然而，導師們轉過身發現是Golden後，所有人都嚇了一跳，連寶兒都說「居然讓這麼有名的人參加比賽」，對此他則表示「因為能讓我好好唱歌的舞台不多，所以才來參加」，得到all pass的好成績更讓到場應援的朋友淚灑攝影棚，大批網友也狂讚「這一次一定要大紅才行」引起許多討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4922/d4922846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4922%2Fd4922846.jpg&h=bb3cbd06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Golden登上《韓國好聲音2020》，導師們爭相按鈕。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n▼影片取自YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=925-kFzbISo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D925-kFzbISo&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=5381a3e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=925-kFzbISo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />JYP真係KPOP清泉"},{"pid":"861a79ec12228c5716e71a080546815e77724b8d","tid":2053322,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T08:51:23.000Z","msg":"善......"}]}